name: Easy Mode
description:
The first song ever between two Brothers, BLS (at age 16) and Jaytheoscillator aka now AnalogueI_O.
The precursor to what is now 
OG Space GOAT, seemed fitting to be the first single. In all its lo-fi, crunchy glory.
"Take a lyric from your mind, fucken stab it."

OG Space GOAT 2022
